Members of the Susquehanna River Art Center of Clearfield (SRACC) received a grant from the Clearfield County Charitable Foundation to support student artwork from the Clearfield Area School District. The result was these beautiful murals, now proudly displayed on the CAST building!

The community is encouraged to attend upcoming events that will be posted on the Susquehanna River Arts Center Facebook page.

The new SRACC center is located next to the The Ritz Theater in downtown Clearfield
